<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Whatever" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Whatever,</orth> no matter what; this or that or any thing that; all that; substantively: <cit><quote>take no repulse, w. she doth say,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.100" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 1, 100</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.330" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 330</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.71" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 71</bibl> (Qq <emph>whate'er</emph>). <bibl n="shak. h5 5.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 8</bibl>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>w. fortune stays him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 23</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 1, 84</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>